headline: Textron Aviation Defense Announces Wichita Production Plans for Beechcraft M-346N If Awarded U.S. Navy’s UJTS Contract
summary: WICHITA, Kan., October 28, 2025--Textron Aviation Defense announced if awarded UJTS program contract by the U.S. Navy, it will assemble Beechcraft M-346N in Wichita, KS.

headline: Danny Maldonado Named President & CEO of Bell
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., October 28, 2025--Danny Maldonado is named president & CEO of Bell, effective January 4, 2026.
